sequenceDiagram
    participant Player as 👤 Player
    participant UI as ⚛️ Web App
    participant GameAPI as 🎮 Game API
    participant Judge as ⚖️ Judge API
    participant WS as 🔌 WebSocket
    participant DB as 🗄️ Database
    
    Note over Player,DB: Card Play Flow with Rule Enforcement
    
    Player->>UI: Select card from hand
    UI->>UI: Highlight selected card
    UI->>UI: Enable "Play Card" button
    
    Player->>UI: Click "Play Card"
    
    alt Card is an 8
        UI->>Player: Show suit selector modal
        Player->>UI: Select suit (hearts/diamonds/clubs/spades)
    end
    
    UI->>UI: Disable UI (loading state)
    UI->>GameAPI: POST /games/{id}/actions/play-card<br/>{cardId, selectedSuit?}
    
    GameAPI->>DB: Validate game state
    DB-->>GameAPI: Current game state
    
    GameAPI->>GameAPI: Validate card play<br/>(matches suit/rank)
    
    alt Invalid card play
        GameAPI-->>UI: 400 Bad Request<br/>{error: "Invalid card"}
        UI->>UI: Show error message
        UI->>UI: Re-enable UI
    else Valid card play
        GameAPI->>Judge: POST /evaluate<br/>{action, context, rules}
        
        Note over Judge: Evaluate against<br/>all active rules
        
        Judge->>Judge: Check each rule's<br/>triggers and conditions
        
        alt Rule violation detected
            Judge-->>GameAPI: {violations: [{ruleId, penalty}]}
            GameAPI->>DB: Apply penalty cards
            GameAPI->>DB: Update player hand
        else No violations
            Judge-->>GameAPI: {violations: []}
        end
        
        GameAPI->>DB: Update game state<br/>(move card, advance turn)
        DB-->>GameAPI: Updated state
        
        GameAPI->>WS: Publish card.played event
        GameAPI->>WS: Publish turn.changed event
        
        alt Penalty applied
            GameAPI->>WS: Publish penalty.applied event
        end
        
        alt Special card effect
            GameAPI->>WS: Publish card.special.effect event
        end
        
        GameAPI-->>UI: 200 OK<br/>{game, penalties}
        
        WS-->>UI: card.played event
        WS-->>UI: turn.changed event
        
        alt Penalty applied
            WS-->>UI: penalty.applied event
            UI->>UI: Show penalty notification
            UI->>UI: Add penalty cards to hand
        end
        
        UI->>UI: Animate card to discard pile
        UI->>UI: Update game state
        UI->>UI: Update turn indicator
        UI->>UI: Re-enable UI
        
        UI->>Player: Show updated game state
    end
    
    Note over Player,DB: All players receive real-time updates via WebSocket